<template>
    <HeaderNav/>
</template>

<script>
import HeaderNav from './Header.vue'
export default {
    name: "ToDo",
    components:{
        HeaderNav
    },
    mounted() {

        const user = localStorage.getItem('user - info')
        if (!user) {
            this.$router.push({ name: 'LogIn' })
        }        
    }
}

</script>
